# WHAT A.U.R.A ACTUALLY IS

A.U.R.A is a real-time AI surveillance and intelligence system.

It is NOT just a website.

It is an AI operating system style platform that:

• Reads live camera feeds
• Detects people, vehicles, and objects using YOLOv8
• Tracks objects across time
• Detects suspicious behavior
• Generates AI narration
• Streams updates in real-time using WebSockets
• Displays everything inside a futuristic intelligence dashboard

The system is split into:

## FRONTEND

Visual interface.
Built using:

• Next.js
• React
• TailwindCSS
• TypeScript

The frontend handles:

• UI
• AI dashboard
• Live surveillance page
• Intelligence panels
• Realtime event feed
• Neural particles
• Ambient AI visuals

---

## BACKEND

AI processing system.
Built using:

• Python
• FastAPI
• YOLOv8
• OpenCV
• WebSockets

The backend handles:

• Camera access
• Object detection
• Tracking
• Suspicious activity detection
• Narration
• Realtime streaming

