# EXPLANATION OF EVERY BACKEND FILE

## camera.py

Handles webcam access.

Reads camera frames using OpenCV.

---

## yolo_engine.py

Loads YOLO model.

Runs object detection.

Returns:

• Labels
• Confidence
• Bounding boxes
• Tracking IDs

---

## tracker.py

Stores object memory.

Tracks:

• First seen
• Last seen
• Duration
• Confidence
• Object box positions

---

## event_engine.py

Analyzes suspicious behavior.

Detects:

• Loitering
• Long presence
• Stationary objects

---

## narrator.py

Creates AI-generated scene summaries.

Turns detections into readable narration.

---

## zone_engine.py

Checks if objects enter specific regions.

Used for:

• Restricted zones
• Danger zones
• Intrusion detection

---

## socket_manager.py

Handles WebSocket realtime communication.

Streams live intelligence to frontend.

---

## main.py

Main FastAPI server.

Controls:

• API routes
• WebSockets
• Video streaming
• Detection pipeline

